name: the city will keep us warm

metadata.name: the city will keep us warm
metadata.description:
This piece is a collaboration between my_art_bytes and Arbour, two Seattle-based artists. It shows a view of Downtown Seattle as a late winter's snow blankets the city.

Art is original and created by my_art_bytes.
All of the music and sound recordings were recorded on location at the corner of Wall St & Alaska Way in Seattle, Washington by Arbour."
